    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'll keep an eye on the weeds. i just meant like... real biological stuff. like do bugs or worms or larvae or anything like that actually cause the nutrients to disappear so fast, or is it usually just chemistry stuff? i'm just worried something is actually eating the roots or something.",
